{
  "page": "The Sons of the Dragon (Gyldayn)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>The Sons of the Dragon</b></i> is a history of Kings <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>. It was written by <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a>, an archmaester of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>. It uses Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen\" title=\"Gawen\">Gawen</a> as a source. A revised version of <i>The Sons of the Dragon</i> was included as a chapter of Gyldayn's history of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood,_Being_a_History_of_the_Targaryen_Kings_of_Westeros\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood, Being a History of the Targaryen Kings of Westeros\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> but the ending of this version provides textual evidence that it was written as a separate, stand-alone work before this.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Sons_of_the_Dragon_(Gyldayn)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214138\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 176/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8585/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 509/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 134/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1095/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   36.314      1 -total\n 76.78%   27.882      1 Template:Italic_title\n 17.46%    6.339      2 Template:Ref\n 10.78%    3.913      2 Template:Ref/core\n  5.06%    1.838      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26267-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404214138 and revision id 328935\n -->\n",
